TCG is in search for a WordPress developer/designer for a 3 month+ assignment near the St. Louis just on the other side of the river. 
Responsibilities:   


Works extensively with WordPress and Adobe Creative Cloud to design and develop web pages and content for our online properties. 

Manage content updates to our online properties. 

Job Requirements 

Minimum 3 years of previous web design experience preferred; 

Strong interactive design and front end development skills; 

High proficiency in Adobe Creative Cloud and Microsoft Office products; 

Extensive knowledge and skills in WordPress; 

High proficiency in JavaScript, HTML5, CSS, jQuery, PHP, SQL; 

Working knowledge of Ektron CMS is a plus;  

Department:  Web Developer
